A video of man’s mouth going on fire, while trying to drink a flaming Lamborghini has gone viral. In the video, the man wearing a white and orange sweater can be seen taking the shot of the flaming Lamborghini from another man seated at the bar. As the man drinks the shot, expecting it to go down well on his throat – the flame at the top of the glass comes into contact with his beard and he goes up in flames. It is not clear, when and where the incident happened. 